# SecureChat Documentation Structure Plan

> A professional, audience-based documentation architecture for sales, clients, developers, and interview preparation.

---

## Overview

This document defines the complete restructuring of SecureChat documentation into **four audience-specific directories** with clear separation of concerns, no content repetition, and professional organization.

---

