- [04_Security_and_Encryption.md](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/documents/Interview/SecureChat/04_Security_and_Encryption.md) → Security questions
- [05_Backend_Design.md](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/documents/Interview/SecureChat/05_Backend_Design.md) → Backend decisions
- [06_Database_and_Data_Modeling.md](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/documents/Interview/SecureChat/06_Database_and_Data_Modeling.md) → Database questions
- [07_Real_Time_Communication.md](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/documents/Interview/SecureChat/07_Real_Time_Communication.md) → WebSocket questions
