- [10_Tradeoffs_and_Lessons.md](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/documents/Interview/SecureChat/10_Tradeoffs_and_Lessons.md) → "What would you do differently?"
- [11_Must_Know_Interview_Questions.md](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/documents/Interview/SecureChat/11_Must_Know_Interview_Questions.md) → Quick reference
- [12_Frequently_Asked_Questions.md](file:///media/swastik/focus/projects%202026/chat%20app/0.0/documents/Interview/SecureChat/12_Frequently_Asked_Questions.md) → Rapid-fire prep

**Anti-Repetition Rule:**
> For technical details, reference `../developer-docs/` files. Interview-prep translates technical knowledge into stories and answers.

